Program: Discovery
Title: The electron's 100th anniversary
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwwk
Last Broadcast Date: 12 May 1997
Celebrating the 100th anniversary of John Joseph Thompson's announcement. A report on the centenary of the discovery of the electron, announced to the Royal Institution in 1897, and what the discovery of the sub atomic particle meant. Presenter: Martin Redfern.